div.div: Baseline and projected percentage contributions to the DRI from total seafood in First Nations by (A) gender and (B) by age groups, under ‘strong mitigation’ (RCP 2.6) and ‘business-as-usual’ (RCP 8.5) climate change scenarios.
div.p: DRI—dietary reference intakes using recommended dietary allowance (RDA) and recommended intake (RI) for EPA+DHA.
